\lim_{n\to\infty}\left(\left(1 + \frac{\sin n}{5n + 1}\right)^{\frac{1}{\frac{\sin n}{5n + 1}}}\right)^{\frac{2n + 3}{5n + 1}\cdot\sin n} &=
